Brown Bear
mm 319; Miscellaneous Creatures|phb 304|dmbr 13
Large beast, unaligned

Armor Class 11 (natural armor)
Hit Points 34 (4d10 + 12)
Speed 40 ft., climb 30 ft.

STR 19 (+4)
DEX 10 (+0)
CON 16 (+3)
INT 2 (-4)
WIS 13 (+1)
CHA 7 (-2)

Skills Perception +3
Senses passive Perception 13
Languages -
Challenge 1 (200 XP)

Keen Smell.
The bear has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on smell.

ACTIONS

Multiattack.
The bear makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its claws.

Bite.
Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 8 (1d8 + 4) piercing damage.

Claws.
Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 11 (2d6 + 4) slashing damage.
